from(bucket: "${Process_Bucket}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "ActuatorOperTimes" and r.StationName == "10N1" and r.DeviceName == "SlideUnitLeft" and r.OperationType =="Extend_T")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._field == "Anomaly_ratio")
